&lt;Peat Marwick>, an accounting andmanagement consulting firm, and &lt;Nolan, Norton and Co>, aninformation and technology planning concern, said they havemerged.    The companies said with the merger Nolan now will be knownas Nolan, Norton and Co-partners, the information technologyarm of Peat Marwick.    Also as part of the merger, Nolan's 21 principals havebecome Peat Marwick partners, the companies said. Reuter&#3;